import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['delay'] = pd.to_numeric(data['delay'], errors='coerce')
    plt.hist(data['delay'], bins=50, color='blue', edgecolor='black')
    plt.axvline(data['delay'].median(), color='red', label='Median: {:.2f}'.format(data['delay'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of delay time?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['distance'] = pd.to_numeric(data['distance'], errors='coerce')
    avg_distance = data['distance'].mean()
    fig, ax = plt.subplots()
    ax.bar('Average Distance', avg_distance, color='blue')
    ax.axhline(avg_distance, color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Average Distance: {avg_distance:.2f}')
    ax.legend()
    plt.title('What is the average distance traveled by flights?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data.dropna(subset=['date'])
    data['year'] = data['date'].dt.year
    data = data.groupby(['origin', 'destination']).agg({'count': 'sum'}).reset_index()
    data = data.pivot(index='origin', columns='destination', values='count')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 10))
    heatmap = ax.pcolor(data, cmap='Blues')
    ax.set_xticks(range(len(data.columns)))
    ax.set_xticklabels(data.columns, rotation=90)
    ax.set_yticks(range(len(data.index)))
    ax.set_yticklabels(data.index)
    plt.colorbar(heatmap)
    plt.title('Which origin and destination pairs are the most common?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd
def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(10, 6))
    ax.boxplot(data['delay'], by=data['origin'])
    ax.set_xlabel('Origin')
    ax.set_ylabel('Delay (minutes)')
    ax.set_title('What is the distribution of delay time by origin?')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.tight_layout()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
